hifiberry-pipewire (1.4.5.3) stable; urgency=low

  * Updated build script to use changelog as single source of truth
  * Improved version consistency and management
  * Added service file for debhelper-compatible systemd integration
  * Enhanced postinst script with idempotent user/group creation
  * Improved systemd service management following Debian best practices
  * Added pipewire group membership for better audio device access
  * Added fix-pipewire-config script to disable problematic D-Bus modules
  * Fixed PipeWire startup errors in headless environments
  * Implemented proper configuration file management with templates
  * Added automatic backup of customized configurations
  * Improved configuration preservation and restoration during upgrades
  * Created configuration override directory for modular settings
  * Optimized build configuration to exclude debug symbols
  * Added explicit symbol stripping and NDEBUG flag for release builds

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Wed, 02 Jul 2025 12:00:00 +0000

